<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Change Address Verification Code</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .email_container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 52px 59px;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Roboto", "Oxygen", "Ubuntu", "Cantarell", "Fira Sans", "Droid Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .token {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Roboto", "Oxygen", "Ubuntu", "Cantarell", "Fira Sans", "Droid Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888888;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email_container">
        <div class="header">
            <img width="100%" src="cid:top_banner">
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>To continue with the address change please enter the following token:</p>
            <div class="token">{{ token }}</div>
            <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email or contact our support team.</p>
            <p>Thank you,<br>The {{ shopName }} Team</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 {{ shopName }}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>